            <li><strong>Performance &amp; Durability (25%):</strong> Evaluates 9 lifetime ratings such as current cycle counts, efficiency, and temperature limits.</li>
            <li><strong>Operational Lifecycle (20%):</strong> Assesses 9 logging fields including C-rate, temperature average, and safety incidents.</li>
